<div class="row">
    <div class="display-container">
        <h1>Challenge Other Players</h1>
        <ol>
            <li>On the home page, select "Challenge Players".</li>
            <li>Select the appropriate contest, and fill out the required fields.
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <b>Start</b>: Choose a start time for the match. If the time is set before the current time, the
                        match will automatically start.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <b>Number of Rounds</b>: The number of rounds to be played for the match. More rounds helps determine
                        which AI is consistently preforming stronger, but may increase the amount of time it takes for it to
                        complete.
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>From the list of available players, select the player you wish to enter into the challenge match, along with
                the player you wish to challenge.</li>
            <li>Select the right arrow to add the players to the challenge match.</li>
            <li>Press the "Challenge!" button.</li>
            <li>The server will start running the challenge match.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</div>